# Summary Annotation
footer_insight: {
  label: |md
    **Architectural Insight:** The `Q @ K^T` operation acts as a parallel lookup mechanism. 
    By scaling by `1/√d_k`, we ensure stable gradients during backpropagation.
  |
  shape: text
  near: bottom-center
  style: {
    font-size: 14
    italic: true
  }
}